    "research_text": "I found no internal contradictions in this summary. All dates are consistent, figures align with their stated time periods, and the narrative progression is logically sound:\n\n- February 6, 2026: Framework for Interim Agreement reached\n- February 13, 2025: BTA negotiations launched (earlier date, appropriate for launch)\n- Early July 2026: Ambassador statement about nearing completion\n- ~4 weeks remaining until August 2026: Consistent with \"early July\" timeframe\n\nThe summary is returned unchanged.",
